ing the animal circle now counts. Each present-human org is charged an additive penalty — farmed-animal life-years caused per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJytWNty2zgS%2FZUu126N5BUlSmNbtlJ%2B8EVOUvHseGPPeHdtlwORkIgRSTAAaJrJ%2BN%2FnANT9Emd29iEVmgBOn25092nq607IhyyPzZkM%2BU5vp9Wi4%2BNjulFMpGQkBYp9KfFQpHSfd%2Fz2HhVSxeGT4AUV7cfO48Fjl2rayIy6dXv0PgXEidZ5khkhUwoiIPXIp4wpGUSCxRaofdShNg2ZemQFKx%2BjPGGpni50iKUiYbF%2B1DLhRcTMdOWAdD4cciXS0eNQBrnm4XSpSwln5hH%2FuHrMlBzEPHFc%2BiyIiM0JCU2MrkoT4XkoYk5wdL6sW2SsQRaGukGKIzoi5ZqkcmCKe%2FCDJRxWhMZ7E%2FHKxR80DfM0cBhvKJBJJjVozjfgbBpyIOKV0A5NG5aGLJYppwThj5v0aRbd%2FtMnS9Ue588ZDwwOPrE45ySHDmF%2BEU0Hdsq1oUFeUm7N2IOaLzrWoxtgvbOR5nTJ2Sjn1cG3%2FX%2F2P57c9M9pUNKIp1whhs2snF44D4VZitAuFhuUSlPxsEEEksP6JQ24MtbbRCpc9SxYutpbRYJlWSy4btJ1mTRjOUqlwnXXvmb7DcqO9l%2FqDstd1JH%2Fdzp7%2F8btHHDDqrf2ftlAxMKAyEBaj0ObrXd%2Bg9oPTbpggZGwyRSvoLAhs%2BFPTYO0JG5zQqoRLq1%2FV5yfXP6n9bcHGvBYFkhKe9ZdLn%2FGc1ziOLARUIcF22EemOoauM26VMP9YSxznIpw5%2BdCB%2BBk6HjdQVRC0z90btrHw5c6kcsrYMKHgotRBGzUjUIq2wSKEC2bgppqNzJhWozf0K9wyK51%2FI6PYM2K4koJUDflZsvtZnti%2BKC5PzHMn41iC2bZE%2B7PQsNnniKDZtjbzbuwnAuFJCWO3YFDWohxplDOqkSAU5RTIPDcoNP%2Bxc8f%2B1WeOISKBHC358W0ImZrVEQSJE0hPS2QBA6oyhm7925y8mGayywFJZSHJ4dewkapMHnI6fTnm%2F4ZEqNMBjIWgcsQxKF0aPaCa%2FVJctjsS1lcGuxCmUSu0ACqWZLFPGxW3abyeihGuUJ7qWp9pCZpavsqXNBIlwCtQdjCtm3JIInwMvsgTBDx9IpLIL7jccbDK65%2B0eHWdNqfpZMrnQWQWx7HA46QvkXZnYP3Vgy%2FPQPx2ysoZzaZubKF